<p><span data-sheets-value="{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;I‚Äôm a frontend UI developer at EPAM. I work in a bigger team, developing an application relying mainly on frontend technologies and designing the user interface. I use HTML, CSS and JavaScript on a daily basis.&quot;}" data-sheets-userformat="{&quot;2&quot;:384,&quot;10&quot;:1,&quot;11&quot;:3}">I think it‚Äôs important to understand that the learning process can‚Äôt really be accelerated. Programming is a big challenge, not easy in the beginning. But once you‚Äôve got the hang of it and understand the logic, it all becomes clear. From that point onwards everything speeds up. <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/13.1.0/72x72/1f642.png" alt="üôÇ" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" />¬†</span></p>
